           :     VisibilityFilterExec: tables=[m]
           :       HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=LeftSemi, on=[(id@1, main_id@0)]
           :         HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=LeftSemi, on=[(id@1, main_id@0)]
           :           CooperativeExec
